---
const roadmap = [
  'Post-processor editing',
  'DNC file transfer',
  'File compare',
  '4/5-axis viz',
];
---
<section class="honesty" id="honesty">
  <div class="container honesty-grid">
    <div class="honesty-left">
      <span class="eyebrow-line">03 · What Beta Doesn't Do</span>
      <h2 class="honesty-title">
        We're honest<br/>about what beta<br/>doesn't do yet.
      </h2>
      <div class="honesty-measure">
        <span class="measure-rule">00 — 003 · Roadmap</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="honesty-right">
      <p class="honesty-p">
        This is a focused v1. We haven't shipped: post-processor editing,
        DNC file transfer, advanced file comparison, or 4th-and-5th-axis
        visualization. Those are on the roadmap.
      </p>
      <p class="honesty-p">
        If you need those today, stay on your current tool — we'd rather
        you wait than be disappointed.
      </p>
      <p class="honesty-p honesty-p-strong">
        If you mostly want a clean editor plus backplot that opens fast
        and doesn't crash on real shop programs, the beta is for you.
      </p>

      <div class="roadmap-chips">
        {roadmap.map((item) => (
          <div class="roadmap-chip">
            <span>{item}</span>
            <span class="roadmap-tag">Roadmap</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .honesty {
    padding: clamp(72px, 10vw, 120px) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line-1);
  }
  .honesty-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
    gap: 72px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .honesty-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 3.6vw, 42px);
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fg-1);
    margin: 18px 0 0;
  }
  .honesty-measure {
    margin-top: 24px;
  }
  .honesty-right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .honesty-p {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--fg-2);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .honesty-p-strong {
    color: var(--fg-1);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .roadmap-chips {
    margin-top: 12px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 10px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fg-4);
  }
  .roadmap-chip {
    border: 1px solid var(--line-2);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--cnc-accent);
    padding: 10px 12px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    background: var(--bg-2);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 8px;
    align-items: center;
    color: var(--fg-2);
    transition: border-color var(--dur-med) var(--ease-std), background var(--dur-med) var(--ease-std);
  }
  .roadmap-chip:hover {
    border-color: var(--cnc-accent);
    background: var(--bg-3);
  }
  .roadmap-tag {
    color: var(--cnc-accent);
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .honesty { padding: 56px 0; }
    .honesty-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
    }
    .honesty-title {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin: 14px 0 0;
    }
    .honesty-p { font-size: 15.5px; }
    .roadmap-chips {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
